snippet.title: Merchants of Rosewall Trailer – PC Gaming Show: Most Wanted 2024
snippet.description:
Merchants of Rosewall is a story driven shopkeeping simulation where you buy and sell stock, manage your employees, and try to keep your business afloat, all while unravelling the mysteries of Rosewall’s elite citizens. https://store.steampowered.com/app/2616800/Merchants_of_Rosewall/
